Name: Путешествие паладина
About the game: This is a story about a paladin that left his home monastery for the first time to go on quest. The quest appeared harder that paladin throught: she is haunted by demons now, and the only people who coul help her - ancient rivals of paladins, the Duids. Dramatic story combining classic JRPG feateures with CRPG one: Choose gender, appearence, background and skills on your hero. Gather your party: six different characters who could join your quest. Weave your fate: non-linear story with different outcomes. Explore the world: find secret places and additional quests.
